    dc:title "Two new species of Calima Moreno-González and Villarreal, 2012 (Arachnida: Schizomida: Hubbardiidae) from the Colombian Andes, with a discussion on the male flagellar microsetae of Hubbardiinae" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5183902>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5183906>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5183910>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5183904>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5183908>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5183916>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5183918> ;
